{"tid":2508847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務院：《入境條例》修訂具潛在用法  ； 中國任意動用出境禁令","createTime":"2021-04-29T05:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T05:38:09.000Z","uid":227801,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a1c3bf383be3ea960d1d9cd0295a240f2c157c","tid":2508847,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/TY3CZ3ACKNETNC33TQDUZ7ELBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FTY3CZ3ACKNETNC33TQDUZ7ELBM%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzfdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=15a62e60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FTY3CZ3ACKNETNC33TQDUZ7ELBM%2F&h=1eabb702\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/TY3CZ3ACKNETNC33TQDUZ7ELBM/</a><br />\n美國務院對條例潛在用法及缺乏監督表關注<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人周四發表聲明，對本港《入境條例》修訂表示「深切關注」，「華府對其（條例）內容、潛在用法、缺乏監督及問責性感關注。華府長時間以來一直擔心中國在沒有適當法律程序下，任意動用出境禁令，包括針對美國的公民。我們對香港當局未來採納類似的任意措施表達深切關注」。聲明亦促港府履行其承諾，列明新修訂條例只適用於入境航班。<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"1cc1f478b2dcc7835d5e79dab37b86b03ac4d754","tid":2508847,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34225b92abce472af20aacebab77b11938868a64","tid":2508847,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"美帝都出聲, 今次真係唔駛走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42441e7e083a60f4d435f70003acc58c40941c9f","tid":2508847,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34225b92abce472af20aacebab77b11938868a64","tid":2508847,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202